snippet.title: Dicionario.widget - Lingua Portuguesa
snippet.description: Dicionario.widget is a Portuguese dictionary widget for Mac OSX. It allows you to search for the meaning of any Portuguese word, to conjugate a verb and to hear the pronunciation of words (text-to-speech). Latest version : 3.2 (June 2012) \- Bugs fixed.

snippet.title: Seldon
snippet.description: Seldon is a C++ library for linear algebra. It provides vectors and matrices: full, sparse, triangular, hermitian, ... It includes interfaces to Blas, Lapack, Mumps, SuperLU and UmfPack. Seldon implements several solvers such as Gmres, BiCgSTAB, Qmr,

snippet.title: Ada 2005 Math Extensions
snippet.description: The Ada 2005 standard defines real and complex matrix and vector operations. Not every possible operation is supported, so for example only symmetric or hermitian matrices can be solved. This project provides extensions to the Standard for GNAT. The software is issued under the GPL Version 3 with the GCC Runtime Library Exception.
